            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301507</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>vivo 早前除了推出旗舰手机 X200 系列外，近期亦发布了新一代主打摄力的中阶机 V50，依然保留了柔光环设计，同时加入了不少新功能，但使用起来感受如何呢？就让 Edward 为大家实试一下吧。</p><h2>vivo V50 开箱直击</h2><p>在为大家分享 vivo V50 的使用体验前，先让 Edward 为大家带来它的开箱直击吧。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00848-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00848-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00848.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是 vivo 最新推出的中阶手机 V50 的包装盒。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00851-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00851-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00851.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者借得的版本是绸缎黑版，规格为 12GB RAM + 512GB ROM。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00855-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00855-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00855.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打开包装盒，就已经见到 vivo V50 的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00857-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00857-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00857.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00859-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00859-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00859.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中层就会见到一个半透明包装袋，当中包含了手机保护套及说明书。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00862-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00862-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00862.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00864-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00864-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00864.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而底层就会见到 SIM 卡槽针、USB-A to USB-C 数据电源线及 90W 电压充电火牛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00868-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00868-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00868.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00870-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00870-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00870.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301522" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00891-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00891-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00891.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至此开箱完成，之后只要撕开手机的包装袋，再长按开关键，就可以开启电源并进行初始设定了。</p><h2>设计典雅手感不俗</h2><p>在设计上，vivo 今次推出的 V50 基本上与上代 V40 相比有九成相似，不过今次除了较沉实的灰黑色版（官方称为绸缎黑）外，还设有采用红色颇抢眼的安卡拉红版，笔者就觉得外观上后者相对地比较吸引。另外两者除了颜色不同外，机揹物料亦有所不同：绸缎黑版采用的是复合板材，而安卡拉红版就采用了玻璃物料，所以后者重量上会重了 10g，不过两者重量也只是 200g 以下，而且机身厚度也只是 7.39mm（绸缎黑）/ 7.57mm（安卡拉红），加上机背边位及机面荧幕均是采用四弧边设计，机身亦不算太阔，所以单手握机操控手感算是不错，即使长时间握机使用仍然舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/011-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/011-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/011.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V50 设有两种颜色版本：绸缎黑及安卡拉红。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/051-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/051-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/051.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当中笔者觉得安卡拉红会更加抢眼吸引，但它设计上较偏向女性化，而且因为机背采用了玻璃物料，所以会相对较厚及重一点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00874-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00874-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00874.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于绸缎黑版本就采用了复合板材作机背，相对地会较薄及轻，但设计上就比较平实，而且较为中性化，较适合男士使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00884-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00884-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00884.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身中框采用了抛光效果的金属物料制造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00882-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00882-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00882.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于边位方面，无论是机面荧幕还是机背均采用四弧边设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301529" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00931-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00931-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00931.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00930-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00930-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00930.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00932-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00932-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00932.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加上机身算轻及薄，所以长时间单手握机问题不大，单手握机操控或打字亦十分舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301532" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00935-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00935-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00935.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而由于机面机背边位均采用弧边设计，所以即使紧握机身亦不觉有界手感，颇为舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301533" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00899-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00899-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00899.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V50 采用了光学荧幕下指纹解锁技术，解锁灵敏度亦算高。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301534" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00896-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00896-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00896.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00893-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00893-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00893.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身右侧设有开关键及音量键，而机底就设有内置喇叭、USB-C 插槽及 SIM 卡槽。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V50 预载了 vivo 自家的 Funtouch OS 15 作业系统。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301537 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-1-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-1-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-1.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301538 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-2-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-2-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-2.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301539 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-3-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-3-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-3.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301540 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-4-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-4-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-4.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲介面设计上与其他 vivo 手机分别不大。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
